TI  - Soil resistance and recovery during neotropical forest succession
T2  - PHILOSOPHICAL TRANSACTIONS OF THE ROYAL SOCIETY B-BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES
KW  - nitrogen
KW  - phosphorus
KW  - carbon
KW  - pH
KW  - bulk density
