TI  - Nesting of the keyhole wasp Pachodynerus nasidens (Latreille, 1812) (Vespidae, Eumeninae) in a nest of a paper wasp (Vespidae, Polistinae)
T2  - JOURNAL OF HYMENOPTERA RESEARCH
