TI  - Strong floristic distinctiveness across Neotropical successional forests
T2  - SCIENCE ADVANCES
KW  - PLANT DIVERSITY
KW  - DISPERSAL
KW  - EVOLUTION
KW  - AMERICA
KW  - LAND
